<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>gramoo.in — जल्द वापस आएंगे</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tiro+Devanagari+Hindi&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --green: #2d6a4f;
      --green-light: #52b788;
      --cream: #fdf8f0;
    }
    body {
      background-color: var(--cream);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      color: #2c2c2c;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }
    .bg-pattern::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      width: 700px; height: 700px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(82,183,136,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
      top: -200px; left: -200px;
      animation: float1 8s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .bg-pattern::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      width: 500px; height: 500px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212,168,67,0.10) 0%, transparent 70%);
      bottom: -150px; right: -150px;
      animation: float2 10s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .bg-pattern { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; }
    .leaf {
      position: fixed;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0.08;
      animation: drift linear infinite;
      user-select: none;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    @keyframes drift {
      0% { transform: translateY(110vh) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0; }
      10% { opacity: 0.08; }
      90% { opacity: 0.08; }
      100% { transform: translateY(-10vh) rotate(360deg); opacity: 0; }
    }
    @keyframes float1 { 0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0)} 50%{transform:translate(40px,30px)} }
    @keyframes float2 { 0%,100%{transform:translate(0,0)} 50%{transform:translate(-30px,-20px)} }
    .card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.2);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 52px 60px;
      max-width: 540px;
      width: 92%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 40px rgba(45,106,79,0.08), 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.9) inset;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease both;
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .logo-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .logo-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--green-light));
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(45,106,79,0.3);
    }
    .logo-text {
      font-family: 'Tiro Devanagari Hindi', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: var(--green);
    }
    .gear-wrap {
      margin: 0 auto 26px;
      width: 76px; height: 76px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0faf4, #e8f5ee);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(82,183,136,0.08);
      font-size: 2rem;
      animation: spin-slow 6s linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes spin-slow { from{transform:rotate(0deg)} to{transform:rotate(360deg)} }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Tiro Devanagari Hindi', serif;
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      color: var(--green);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .divider {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .divider::before, .divider::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(45,106,79,0.15);
    }
    .divider span {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--green-light);
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .status-list {
      list-style: none;
      text-align: left;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .status-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: #555;
      background: rgba(45,106,79,0.04);
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--green-light);
    }
    .dot {
      width: 8px; height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--green-light);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}
      50%{opacity:0.4;transform:scale(0.7)}
    }
    .contact { font-size: 0.84rem; color: #888; }
    .contact a {
      color: var(--green);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(45,106,79,0.4);
    }
    .badge {
      margin-top: 28px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--green-light));
      color: white;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 6px 18px;
      border-radius: 100px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-pattern"></div>
  <div class="leaf" style="left:10%;animation-duration:14s;animation-delay:0s;font-size:2rem;">🌿</div>
  <div class="leaf" style="left:30%;animation-duration:18s;animation-delay:3s;">🍃</div>
  <div class="leaf" style="left:55%;animation-duration:12s;animation-delay:6s;font-size:1rem;">🌱</div>
  <div class="leaf" style="left:78%;animation-duration:16s;animation-delay:1s;font-size:2.2rem;">🌿</div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="logo-wrap">
      <div class="logo-icon">🌾</div>
      <div class="logo-text">gramoo</div>
    </div>

    <div class="gear-wrap">⚙️</div>

    <h1>रखरखाव जारी है</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      हम gramoo.in को और बेहतर बनाने के लिए<br/>कुछ जरूरी काम कर रहे हैं।<br/>
      जल्द ही वापस आएंगे!
    </p>

    <div class="divider"><span>क्या हो रहा है</span></div>

    <ul class="status-list">
      <li><span class="dot"></span> नई सुविधाएं जोड़ी जा रही हैं</li>
      <li><span class="dot"></span> कुछ bugs ठीक किए जा रहे हैं</li>
      <li><span class="dot"></span> बेहतर अनुभव के लिए अपडेट हो रहा है</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="badge">🌾 &nbsp;gramoo.in — जल्द मिलते हैं</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
